{
    "title": "Bom dia tristeza",
    "artist": "Adoniran Barbosa",
    "composer": "Adoniran Barbosa/Vinicius de Moraes",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Bom dia tristeza, que tarde tristeza, você veio hoje me ver</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7/5-\">Em7/5-</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Já estava ficando até meio triste de estar tanto tempo longe de você</span>\n                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7/5-\">Em7/5-</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7/5-\">Am7/5-</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se chegue tristeza, se sente comigo aqui       nesta mesa de bar</span>\n                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Beba do meu copo, me de o seu ombro que é para eu chorar</span>\n                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Chorar de tristeza, tristeza de amar</span>\n",
